These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, classical, metal, punk
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal | classical | jazz | punk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, pony, ferret, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | frog | ferret | pony | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading, traveling, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | traveling | magic-tricks | reading | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, taxi, subway
1. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | taxi | quad-bike | bus | subway |

 #################################

 
